Get started with

```
go install github.com/bazelbuild/bazelisk@latest
```

An attempt at having a single location to build all the development tools that I
use, so that it's reproducible and all self-contained. Might also help with
setting up in a new environment. However, these tools tend to have specialized
build procedures that each require effort to convert to a Bazel-based build.
Moreover these tools have to be installed on the user's system, so other tools
like CMake are much better suited for this.
